<div id="review_1297122625" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1297122625" />
    <a title="Philomena Callan Cheekypee" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7588197-philomena-callan-cheekypee"><img alt="Philomena Callan Cheekypee" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1576863645p2/7588197.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1297122625?book_show_action=true">Jun 02, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Philomena Callan Cheekypee" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Philomena Callan Cheekypee" href="/user/show/7588197-philomena-callan-cheekypee">Philomena Callan Cheekypee</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1297122625" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13421157410136288406">This is a brilliant anthology. It&apos;s a great chance to meet new authors and read books from authors you already love. Here&apos;s my reviews of a few books included in this anthology. <br/><br/><br/>Royal Blood<br/>This was a really fantastic read. I started this one evening and stayed up until Id finished it as its unputdownable. <br/><br/>I love a good biker story. I also love dark reads so I was super excited to read this. <br/>Mercy and X are the main characters. The attraction between them is instant. Mercy is a feisty character. </span>
  <span id="freeText13421157410136288406" style="display:none">This is a brilliant anthology. It's a great chance to meet new authors and read books from authors you already love. Here's my reviews of a few books included in this anthology. <br /><br /><br />Royal Blood<br />This was a really fantastic read. I started this one evening and stayed up until Id finished it as its unputdownable. <br /><br />I love a good biker story. I also love dark reads so I was super excited to read this. <br />Mercy and X are the main characters. The attraction between them is instant. Mercy is a feisty character. She's got secrets and is on the run. X is dark and twisted. <br /><br />Be warned this is a dark read. If you like raw dark stories then this could be the book for you. This is the beginning of what looks like a very promising series. I'm so looking forward to reading more from this author about these characters.<br /><br />Angel Falling <br /><br />This is book one in this three part series. All the books in this series can be read as standalones. <br /><br />This is a really great read. Aspen and Hank are great main characters. Hanks a really sexy cowboy. When Hank saves Aspens life both their lives change. The chemistry between these two is brilliant. <br /><br />I found this to be a really intense rollercoaster of a story. Brilliant story that I highly recommend.<br /><br />Letting Go<br /><br />What a brilliant debut book this was.<br />Cassidy has been through a lot yet she's come out the other side smiling. James is the oh so hot millionaire playboy. This is their story. It's a totally hot book with lots of sex in it. I loved the storyline. Although the POV changed a lot I totally loved this book. It doesn't end in a cliff hanger but there is certainly more to their story. <br />Received in return for an honest review.<br /><br />Irrevocable<br /><br />Where do I start with this review? Can you just look in my head and see the jumble mess the author just left me in?? No ok I'll try and put into words what I thought. <br /><br />This book is what it says in the synopsis... Plus so much more. Its a really dark story that's gonna have you thinking 'what the hell am I reading'. I sat and read this in one sitting. It got under my skin. On several occasions I shaked my head thinking how can I seriously like reading this book. Yes it's that kinda book. <br /><br />This is a phenomenal written by a fantastic author.<br /><br />Warning: This isn't your rainbows and love sonnets kind of romance. This story explores topics of abduction and slavery, and contains explicit scenes of graphic violence and (non-con/dub-con) sex.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="13421157410136288406" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
