        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1318779452" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15559399519442974079">Holy crap on a cracker......<br/>This anthology is a serious work of art! Wether you have a romantic streak or you are a naughty reader - you will find it all in this one HOT package!<br/>My favorite book in this collection has to be &apos;The Descendant&apos; by Kelley Grealis!<br/>I have a soft spot for this book, it is the first book I read and reviewed on my blog, Dowie&apos;s Place! <br/>The beginning has a slow build that did seem to take a little longer than necessary to get through. For that reason, the start of the story</span>
  <span id="freeText15559399519442974079" style="display:none">Holy crap on a cracker......<br />This anthology is a serious work of art! Wether you have a romantic streak or you are a naughty reader - you will find it all in this one HOT package!<br />My favorite book in this collection has to be 'The Descendant' by Kelley Grealis!<br />I have a soft spot for this book, it is the first book I read and reviewed on my blog, Dowie's Place! <br />The beginning has a slow build that did seem to take a little longer than necessary to get through. For that reason, the start of the story was slightly difficult to relate to. However once it got going there was never a dull moment! We have a Biblical Based work of fiction that will not stop!<br />We find our heroine at an emotional crossroads searching for answers and fresh out of tragedy, she's suddenly thrown into a world she couldn't have possibly imagined. She seems to acclimate rather quickly, almost too quickly, and too soon we find the story has finished. I wanted more!!<br />I love the different take on the history of the siblings and vampirism. It's refreshing to read something different that still stays true to the genre yet can still be entertaining.<br />If you like a strong female lead, coming into her own while struggling to find her place, then this is most assuredly a good read.<br />All of these books are fantastic! If you are looking for betrayal stories, warrior, or something more on the naughty side- Indulgence is THE book - books ;) - for you!<br />~Dowie</span>
  <a data-text-id="15559399519442974079" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
