  <span id="freeText6796392903755574885" style="display:none">~*~ Obsessed by books copy given in exchange for an honest review ~*~<br /><br />This box set grabbed my attention as it had not one but two of my favourite authors and I thought hmmmm who have they climbed into bed with now? I had to check this anthology out! Trusting that they would not lead me astray I was overwhelmed by the quality and variety of this box set. New to many of the authors I was truly amazed by the content as each full length novel is a mighty fine read. I found myself devouring each story like a kid in a candy shop. <br /><br />This anthology has a little of everything to please all die hard fans of romance, erotica and paranormal love. I was shocked at how much I actually enjoyed the cowboy read, as this isn't my usual but this anthology has taught me to broaden my horizons and embrace the cowboys! My to be read list has grown exponentially. A marvelous introduction to 15 wickedly talented authors that may have otherwise escaped my attention. This is one of the most perfect box sets I have. I really can't find the words do it justice! <br /><br />A five star aptly named anthology that everyone should read.</span>
