<span id="freeTextContainer11159376921191708645">This is a wonderful collection from a group of hugely talented authors. There is something for everyone. If you&apos;re into contemporary romance, MC&apos;s, paranormal, dark romance, cowboys, BDSM. This anthology offers it all. Plus I was able to discover a few new authors who I will be following their work for more.<br/>My favorite was The Descendant by Kelley Grealis it&apos;s the first part of the Descendant Vampire Series and I definitely want to read the rest of this series. Also this author is new to me, and</span>
  <span id="freeText11159376921191708645" style="display:none">This is a wonderful collection from a group of hugely talented authors. There is something for everyone. If you're into contemporary romance, MC's, paranormal, dark romance, cowboys, BDSM. This anthology offers it all. Plus I was able to discover a few new authors who I will be following their work for more.<br />My favorite was The Descendant by Kelley Grealis it's the first part of the Descendant Vampire Series and I definitely want to read the rest of this series. Also this author is new to me, and I just love her writing style, and her take on the vampire is really something else, a totally unique twist on vampires. I was immersed into this story right away, it is just really gripping.<br />Royal Blood by Amity Cross was another one that just gripped on to me and wouldn't let go. This one is dark and a total hang on to your seat read. There's just so much good reading here. You just aren't going to find a better collection. You get more bang for your buck with this anthology, it's really a gift from these authors. I was given a complimentary copy of this book in exchange for an honest review.</span>
