<span id="freeTextContainer2444241048082669968">This anthology contains a wide variety of different genres by many authors. This anthology has 15 full length stories with something for everyone from Cowboys to Bikers, Vampires and more. These are the reviews for my favorite books in the collection.<br/><br/>Amity Cross Royal Blood (Royal Blood #1)<br/><br/>I really enjoyed this book although it was kind of and MC book it was kind of not. The MC part of the story wasn’t the focus of the story, the search for X’s mark and Mercy’s past are the main focus of the sto</span>
  <span id="freeText2444241048082669968" style="display:none">This anthology contains a wide variety of different genres by many authors. This anthology has 15 full length stories with something for everyone from Cowboys to Bikers, Vampires and more. These are the reviews for my favorite books in the collection.<br /><br />Amity Cross Royal Blood (Royal Blood #1)<br /><br />I really enjoyed this book although it was kind of and MC book it was kind of not. The MC part of the story wasn’t the focus of the story, the search for X’s mark and Mercy’s past are the main focus of the story with the MC theme around the edge which I really liked. The book ends on a cliffhanger so i’m excited to find out what happens to the couple in the next book.<br /><br />Audrey Carlan Angel Falling (Falling #1)<br /><br />Loved the story! Loved Hank and Aspen. Hank seriously makes me want to go searching for guys in Texas! Hihi, Aspen was so sweet though I’m glad she loosened up by the end of the book. I’m glad he fought for her and that Aspen’s friend were on her side. A really great romance that proves that no matter where you come from love trumps all.<br /><br />Cynthia Sax Releasing Rage<br /><br />I LOVED this book! This was my first cyborg book and it was amazing. I loved the characters the plot everything! There was an equal amount of plot and naughty goodness which I loved. Rage and Joan are awesome I’m amazed I liked her with a name like Joan seems an odd choice for the h’s name but it works it describes her character perfectly and Rage’s name is so cool and also fits his personality. Really good book.<br /><br />Deanndra Hall My Last Dom<br /><br />This book was great! Both of the main characters have had bad past relationships and struggle to find someone they can trust. There is a lot of things going on in this story and you’ll be hooked from the start. There’s great sex and the story makes you want to keep reading to find out what will happen to the new couple. There is a moment where things look bleak but then they managed to turn out well.<br /><br />Laura Harner Rescued (Three’s allowed 2)<br /><br />I really enjoyed this book. It was emotional and sexy. The characters were perfect for each other and I love that they had to find out who they were as people before jumping into a relationship together. The action was great the sex hot and the story was great.<br /><br />Skye Callahan Irrevocable (Irrevocable 1)<br /><br />This book was great! I wasn’t sure what to expect but if you like a dark read this is the story for you. I won’t say anything because I don’t want to spoil the story but it was really good and the characters are awesome. I felt for Silver from the beginning and at first I hated Kirk but near the end of the book he started to grow on me and his actions in the beginning of the book became clear. A very good story that I really enjoyed and will have to read the sequel.<br /><br />Theresa Troutman A special Connection<br /><br />It’s hard to put into words what this story is about but if I had to try I’d say it’s a story about love and lose and finding your forever with someone that’s made for you. A really nice story.<br /><br /> </span>
