              <span id="reviewTextContainer1298736572" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13669146352382362461">This is one bad a$$ anthology. Overflowing with awesomeness. If you want a variety of Romance this is the anthology to buy! There is something for everyone, Rockstars, Bikers, Hitmen, Dom&apos;s, Soccer Celebrities, Cowboys, Deviant&apos;s, Navy Seals, Sexy Cyborg&apos;s, Billionaires and more.<br/><br/>What really made this anthology stand out from all the others for me is that all the books are FULL LENGTH books, not novella&apos;s/novelette&apos;s, but full blown books - can&apos;t beat a deal like that! <br/> <br/><br/>Merged review:<br/><br/>This is one </span>
  <span id="freeText13669146352382362461" style="display:none">This is one bad a$$ anthology. Overflowing with awesomeness. If you want a variety of Romance this is the anthology to buy! There is something for everyone, Rockstars, Bikers, Hitmen, Dom's, Soccer Celebrities, Cowboys, Deviant's, Navy Seals, Sexy Cyborg's, Billionaires and more.<br /><br />What really made this anthology stand out from all the others for me is that all the books are FULL LENGTH books, not novella's/novelette's, but full blown books - can't beat a deal like that! <br /> <br /><br />Merged review:<br /><br />This is one bad a$$ anthology. Overflowing with awesomeness. If you want a variety of Romance this is the anthology to buy! There is something for everyone, Rockstars, Bikers, Hitmen, Dom's, Soccer Celebrities, Cowboys, Deviant's, Navy Seals, Sexy Cyborg's, Billionaires and more.<br /><br />What really made this anthology stand out from all the others for me is that all the books are FULL LENGTH books, not novella's/novelette's, but full blown books - can't beat a deal like that! <br /> <br /><br />Merged review:<br /><br />This is one bad a$$ anthology. Overflowing with awesomeness. If you want a variety of Romance this is the anthology to buy! There is something for everyone, Rockstars, Bikers, Hitmen, Dom's, Soccer Celebrities, Cowboys, Deviant's, Navy Seals, Sexy Cyborg's, Billionaires and more.<br /><br />What really made this anthology stand out from all the others for me is that all the books are FULL LENGTH books, not novella's/novelette's, but full blown books - can't beat a deal like that! <br /> <br /><br />Merged review:<br /><br />This is one bad a$$ anthology. Overflowing with awesomeness. If you want a variety of Romance this is the anthology to buy! There is something for everyone, Rockstars, Bikers, Hitmen, Dom's, Soccer Celebrities, Cowboys, Deviant's, Navy Seals, Sexy Cyborg's, Billionaires and more.<br /><br />What really made this anthology stand out from all the others for me is that all the books are FULL LENGTH books, not novella's/novelette's, but full blown books - can't beat a deal like that!</span>
