    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Darlene by: </span>
      Drue Hoffman
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6997958-darlene?shelf=arc">arc</a>
