      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1310014722" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1755468764615687993">If you have not picked up Indulgence yet, you do not know what you are missing. This collection is so underpriced that you would not believe it. I knew during the first story, that this was going to be an awesome collection and I was not wrong. If you are looking for a collection of short stories, this is not the one for you. These are full length books written by fabulous authors.<br/>Are they all hot and steamy, pretty much, but there is some sweetness and romance thrown in. I lost a lot of sleep r</span>
  <span id="freeText1755468764615687993" style="display:none">If you have not picked up Indulgence yet, you do not know what you are missing. This collection is so underpriced that you would not believe it. I knew during the first story, that this was going to be an awesome collection and I was not wrong. If you are looking for a collection of short stories, this is not the one for you. These are full length books written by fabulous authors.<br />Are they all hot and steamy, pretty much, but there is some sweetness and romance thrown in. I lost a lot of sleep reading this because I just could not put it down. I cannot write a review about each individual story here because then the review would just be too long.<br />These are not cookie cutter stories that feel like you are reading the same story over and over. Each one is unique and attention grabbing. Pick up a copy for yourself and prepare to be thoroughly entertained. <br />This is for sure a 5 ***** read for me. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="1755468764615687993" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
