        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1332377729" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17544918270570368766">I was given this book collection to read for an honest review. This was my first time reading an Anthology, and I loved it. 15 Books by 15 different authors, Each book is written by a new author and each has there own story line, yet they are great to read in there own way. From reading an Anthology, I came across you come to like many new authors in your reading to look into and read more of there published books. This collection of books was hard to put down and a must needed book collection f</span>
  <span id="freeText17544918270570368766" style="display:none">I was given this book collection to read for an honest review. This was my first time reading an Anthology, and I loved it. 15 Books by 15 different authors, Each book is written by a new author and each has there own story line, yet they are great to read in there own way. From reading an Anthology, I came across you come to like many new authors in your reading to look into and read more of there published books. This collection of books was hard to put down and a must needed book collection for avid romance novel readers. This collection also has a wide variety of Genres to choose from and which, will also open your eyes to new genres you may have not thought of trying to read or didn't want to read. After reading this collection you may come across a new Genre you like. The books are very suspenseful and keeps you reading to the end of the collection. This is a great bargain as well for any book reader. </span>
